OL,8,GNice cheery note for Christmas.        
OL,9,B                                       
OL,10,EBOB THE FISHBAlright. I'm sorry I seem 
OL,11,Bto have caused a huge trend in people  
OL,12,Bwriting in and commending Blue Raisan. 
OL,13,GYes. You are totally, irrefutably to   
OL,14,Gblame. That is what you wanted us to   
OL,15, say, isn't it?                         
OL,17,EQUANTUM SHEEPBMerry Xmas. (I'll post   
OL,18,Byou a fiver if you make me 'Ziner of   
OL,19,Bthe year!)GAbsolutely not.             
