OL,5,EDEAR PEOPLE              S /--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BIf I ruled the world:                  
OL,8,BAll lads would have blue or green hair.
OL,9,BChris Evans would ask his guests       
OL,10,Bquestions that aren't about money or   
OL,11,Bboobs.                                 
OL,12,BDennis Pennis would have his own TV    
OL,13,Bstation.                               
OL,14,BBrian Molko and Billie-Joe Armstrong   
OL,15,Bwould be my mum and dad.               
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17,BSo now you know.                       
OL,19,EZero (watching Robin)                  
