OL,5,EDEAR 'ZINERS             S /--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,7,BI have noticed recently how most       
OL,8,Bpeople seem to be going crazy over the 
OL,9,Bstrange race of beings known as the    
OL,10,BTellytubbies. Am I the only person on  
OL,11,Bthis planet who thinks these alien     
OL,12,Btype geezers are not actually that     
OL,13,Bgood?                                  
OL,15,BNow Pingu, THERE'S a good character -  
OL,16,Bfunny, intelligent, original - oh yes, 
OL,17,Bhe could take Po in a fight and no     
OL,18,Bmistake.                               
OL,19,EFozzie (Spice Boy 1)                   
