OL,5,EDEAR 'ZINERS             S /--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,6,BI'm sure that some of you regularly    
OL,7,Bwatch, or are aware of, the Ricki Lake 
OL,8,Bshow. Why then has nobody mentioned the
OL,9,Bcheesy opening titles? They're         
OL,10,Bsickening. Various shots of Ricki      
OL,11,Bprancing around, shopping, jumping into
OL,12,Bconvertibles, giving high fives etc.   
OL,14,BIt's also set to really irritating     
OL,15,Bmusic and, if you listen closely, you  
OL,16,Bcan hear the chants "Go Ricki" in the  
OL,17,Bbackground. Disgusting. I'd like to    
OL,18,B"kick HER to the kerb" erm "girlfriend"
OL,19,ELittle Miss Molko (Brian lover)        
